title: Dizzy Gillespie, Stan Getz, Sonny Stitt - For Musicians Only 195
description:
For Musicians Only is the epitome of the bebop movement. 
Dizzy Gillespie is joined on the front line by Stan Getz and Sonny Stitt for a blowing session of phenomenal proportions.  
An incredible album from start to finish.



STAN GETZ, DIZZY GILLESPIE, SONNY STITT

For Musicians Only   1957



CD / Verve / 320Kbps



Tracklist: 
1 Bebop 	 
2 Dark Eyes 	 
3 Wee (Allen's Alley) 	 
4 Lover Come Back To Me 	 
5 Dark Eyes (Alternate Take)	


Personnel:
Dizzy Gillespie - trumpet
Sonny Stitt - alto sax
Stan Getz - tenor sax
John Lewis - piano
Herb Ellis - guitar
Ray Brown - bass
Stan Levey - drums


Recorded October 16, 1956 in Los Angeles
